@node Important "Important"

   @{u}You really don't know?@{uu}

   Warning! @{b}Leave enabled Miami's log  option@{ub}.  Freedom Call will read
it when importing data. Never close one Miami's connection through "close
the window" boot! Use always "offline" option,  that  avoids  lack  of
information in Miami's log. 
  
   * This version only supports integration with Miami;

   Freedom Call requers assign to it's directory.

   @{"Please read installation help" link Installation}
 
   This program is tested with Miami 2x, 3x, deluxe.

@endnode

@node HowItWorks "I wonder how it works..."

   @{u}How it works?@{uu}

   This program was created to provide statistics for a perfect  time
and charges control on using Internet. It works on Workbench with  GUI
(@{b}Graphical User Interface@{ub}), allowing easy data  manipulation in  all
options.

   @{b}At starting this program, you must import Miami log`s file data.@{ub}

   This importation will generate all files on  Freedom  Call`s  work
database directory, which will have your connection`s data since  the
beginning of log`s use until the present day.
  
   Files generated:
   
   Example:
   Freedom.01.1999  --> Regular and Irregular Calls, for month 01.1999;
   Freedom.02.1999  --> Regular and Irregular Calls, for month 02.1999;
   Freedom.03.1999  --> Regular and Irregular Calls, for month 03.1999;
   Freedom.04.1999  --> Regular and Irregular Calls, for month 04.1999;
   Freedom.Input    --> Calls of manual inputation;
   Freedom.Out      --> ShutDown Online Calls;

   After you import database  until  the present  day,  you  may  run
more forms of Freedom`s database atualization. It's  possible  to  use
generation option day by day, or to  use  @{"FreeEventMiami" link FreeEvent},  a  program
developed for automatic atualization of Freedom's  database.  It's  real
time,  native.  With  FreeEventMiami  you  consult  all  informations
without  any  data  generation, because  this  program  atualizes  and
controls Freedom Call`s database.

   @{"Please read installation help for install FreeEventMiami" link Installation}

   Note: Verify your configuration to optimize this option.

   @{u}Programs@{uu}

   Freedom Call   -> Main program, generates all statistics here;
   Explore Call   -> Little program, only for stats of actual call;
   FreeEventMiami -> Program that integrates realtime Freedom and Miami;

@endnode

@node Req "What it needs?"

   @{u}Requirements@{uu}

   * An Amiga AGA or ECS;
   * Workbench 2.0+;
   * MUI 3.X installed;
   * Miami 2x, 3x, deluxe + with log`s option enabled;
   * 2 Megabytes memory (we recommend more);

@endnode

@node Features "What it can do?"

   @{u}Features@{uu}
   
   This program offers the following options, supported on  general,
daily, monthly or anual refers, defined by the user:

   * Realtime integration with Miami 2x, 3x, Deluxe dialup;
   * How many Internet's calls you made;
   * The wholeness of time on line;
   * Time on line average;
   * Cost of any call;
   * Cost average;
   * How many disconnections you made;
   * How many times the line fell off;
   * How many times your computer was reseted during a connection;
   * Phone, date and duration time of larger connection; 
   * Phone, date and duration time of smaller connection; 
   * Monthly control of connection's time limit; 
   * First and last call in the selected consultation;
   * First and last date in the selected consultation;
   * Control of remaining time in the present month. 
   * Visualization of exceeded conecction's time, based on your limit 
     of hours; 
   * Calls, time online and percentage by week`s day;
   * It allows to visualize its last five Web`s connections (shortcut
     window);
   * It allows to visualize all Web`s connections;
   * It allows to consult about one period of time;
   * Set your free hours;
   * Set your day of initial month;
   * Set number to ignore in statistics;
   * Select limits of your telephone company;
   * Possibility to visualize your telephone costs in current money of
     other country;
   * Provider bill;
   * Provider extra hours cost;
   * Total costs for month;
   * Time, Date, Cost, Online, Speed Connection, protocols of actual
     call;
   * Possibility of visualize your rates on all your connections;
   * Generate all statistics in html format;
   * Support generation in html format to intranets;

   @{" Menu Options " link Menu} @{" Windows Features " link Windows} @{" Configuration " link Configuration}

@endnode

@node Usage "How to use it?"

   @{u}Usage@{uu}

   @{b}CHECK COSTS@{ub} : This option allows your currency month 
                 information about costs;

   @{b}THIS MONTH@{ub}  : It allows data's consultations on the average month; 

   @{b}OTHER MONTH@{ub} : It selects other day, month or  year  to   statistics
                 consultation;

   @{b}GLOBAL@{ub}      : It selects general statistics for all connections;
  
   @{b}ANUAL@{ub}       : It allows data`s consutaions for year;

   @{b}LAST CALLS@{ub}  : This option allows  you  to  consult  its  last  five
                 Web`s connections, with  date,  hour  of  connection,
                 time online and number of telephone.

   @{b}PREFS@{ub}       : Activates configuration's screen; 

   @{b}ABOUT@{ub}       : Shows program's informations; 

   @{" Menu Options " link Menu} @{" Windows Features " link Windows} @{" Configuration " link Configuration}

@endnode

